name: Soldier-up Designs Projects Repository
body:
## Welcome to Soldier-up Designs Github Repository 

Here you will find all my projects I am working on. Keep in mind that they are test projects and may not be complete builds 
(Thanks to Windows *.1 Stripping files on transfers)

want a project simply clone it to your desktop.

1. navigate cmd.exe on your PC and right-click then select run as administrator
2. Then navigate to the directory you want by typing in
     $ cd C:/file/path/you/want/as/parent/
     + then type in:
     $ git clone "https://github.com/blayderunner123/repository.git"
     + then press [ENTER]
     + Then watch it flow (could take a few minutes to complete) Be patient!!
     
### A few things to note **Most** require both [NodeJS](http://nodejs.org/download/) and [Bower](http://bower.io/) to build projects. 

###Other Operating Systems:

1. If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Designer Templates
We've crafted some great projects and would love your feedback and input. **Remember:** when it come to open-source when only develop by the collaboration of other. Like what you see? Well join me and we can build a better Application for a better World Wide Web.

### Authors and Contributors
@blayderunner123 - Owner, Proprietor, Web Designer of [Soldier-up Designs](http://soldierupdesigns.com).
